===Uruguay vs Spain===
The teams have previously met ten times, including twice in the World Cup: a [[1950 FIFA World Cup final round#Uruguay vs Spain|2–2 final round draw]] in [[1950 FIFA World Cup|1950]] and a [[1990 FIFA World Cup Group E#Uruguay vs Spain|0–0 group stage draw]] in [[1990 FIFA World Cup|1990]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Uruguay vs. Spain Head-to-Head in the World Cups|url=https://www.thesoccerworldcups.com/head_to_head/uruguay_vs_spain.php|website=thesoccerworldcups.com|access-date=6 December 2025}}</ref> Their latest encounter was [[2013 FIFA Confederations Cup Group B#Spain vs Uruguay|Spain's 2–1 group stage victory]] at the [[2013 FIFA Confederations Cup]] to keep their unbeaten head to head record.<ref>{{cite web|title=Uruguay national football team: record v Spain|url=https://www.11v11.com/teams/uruguay/tab/opposingTeams/opposition/Spain|website=11v11.com|access-date=December 6, 2025}}</ref>

